milestones.description: Romaine has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (82) in an innings in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Dean Minors's 26
Romaine has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (5) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Lionel Cann's 2
Steven Outerbridge and Kwame Tucker's 28-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 21 between Clay Smith and Steven Outerbridge
Romaine and Mukuddem's 52-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 48 between Tucker and Mukuddem
Clay Smith and Romaine's 68-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 18 between Dean Minors and Tucker
Ian Billcliff and Codrington's 29-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 27 between John Vaughan and Tariq Javed
Romaine has broken the record for most sixes (5) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Lionel Cann's 2
Lionel Cann has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Hasan Durham's 3
Romaine's 101 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for BMUDA), surpassing Romaine's 62
Steven Welsh has conceded the most runs in an innings (68) in ODIs for CAN, going past Seebaran's record of 61
This is the highest match aggregate (533) involving teams Bermuda & Canada in ODIs
Clay Smith and Romaine's 68-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 65 between Gibbons and Romaine
Hasan Durham has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for BMUDA, going past Mukuddem
Ashish Bagai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (12) for CAN, going past John Davison

stories.title: Hasan Durham reported for potentially flawed action
stories.subTitle: Bermuda in Canada 2006
stories.seoTitle: Hasan Durham reported for potentially flawed action
stories.summary: Hasan Durham, Bermuda's left-arm spinner, has been reported for a potentially flawed action after the second ODI against Canada in Toronto, the ICC confirmed

stories.title: Romaine completes Canada's wretched campaign
stories.subTitle: Canada v Bermuda, 2nd ODI, Toronto
stories.summary: Bermuda completed a 2-0 series win over Canada with an 11-run win at the Toronto Cricket, Skating and Curling Club, inflicting the fourth defeat in four ODI matches played by the Canadians in the last month
